00:01:47.830 --> 00:01:51.450
A Bug’s Life
A Bug’s Life is one of Disney Pixar’s

00:01:51.450 --> 00:01:54.870
oldest movies, but that doesn’t mean it
isn’t just as good as the newer films.

00:01:54.870 --> 00:01:58.960
Along with quality storytelling and some fun
characters, the movie also showcases Pixar’s

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:02.159
famous talent for slipping adult jokes into
their kid’s films.

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:06.200
In one scene from the movie, a bunch of bugs
are gathered to watch girl bugs perform.

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:08.840
One of the raunchier bugs yells out from the
audience yells out to the girl on stage, saying:

00:02:08.840 --> 00:02:13.099
“Hey cutie, wanna pollinate with a real
