Peter Pan
Peter Pan is a classic Disney movie and follows

00:03:40.590 --> 00:03:43.580
the story of a young flying boy who never
wants to grow up.

00:03:43.580 --> 00:03:47.180
Well, it turns out that the movie actually
featured a pretty adult moment that you definitely

00:03:47.180 --> 00:03:49.319
had to be grown up to catch.

00:03:49.319 --> 00:03:52.769
Near the beginning of the film, Peter is dancing
around in front of his shadow and if you pause

00:03:52.769 --> 00:03:58.049
the movie at right time you can see that his
shadow has his…uhm…”peter” hanging

00:03:58.049 --> 00:03:59.049
